Template generated automatically during model training.

Templates, except those assigned the golden signal type Information, are used when modeling and tracking log message activity. You can change the name, golden signal type, and state of this template.Learn more
Optionally provide a name to uniquely identify this template. If you do not provide a name, the name will be the same as the log message pattern.
